metadata.description:
"iphone screen" by iman europe.
art by the great andre oshea. 
produced by goodbyecalev, who just won a grammy for coproducing "heated" by beyonce!

in celebration of Black History Month, this is the 1st release from my "5 mints in february" collection. collect at least 3 $IEXBHM tokens to attend my livestream show on 2/28/23 featuring special guests.

a portion of the proceeds from this series will go towards funding The Homies DAO, the new artist-first, wellness-focused DAO that I founded earlier this month.

grateful for your support always. now let's get into the most important part of it all— the lyrics. this song is a reminder to not be blinded by the facade of social media. share it with a friend if you resonate. love y'all. be easy on you.
